rawContent:
Quick reflection on my experience with depression:

Anytime I felt down and sluggish, I was stagnant. Watching TV, scrolling, snoozing my alarm.

Anytime I felt present and energized, I was moving. Walking, lifting, yoga.

Simple but clear message: MOVE!

#depression
